        <mxCell id="-fp5AD1cwv2DQiWJSyQd-1" parent="1" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;overflow=hidden;rounded=0;" value="&lt;h1 style=&quot;margin-top: 0px;&quot;&gt;Manage Stock In Warehouse&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;p&gt;An Employee can add a stock to a warehouse based on a list of available products. When added the employee is prompted to assign a value to the Quantity in stock and the local price at the warehouse. After input and accept the use can view the new stock in the warehouse list.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;An employee can the view a list of stock in a warehouse click on the indvidual stocks to edit the Quantity and price in the warehouse. After edit the list are updated to reflect new reality.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;An employee can remove a product stock from a warehouse, but only when the stock has been reduced to zero. The employee is prompted with a warning about deletion.&lt;/p&gt;" vertex="1">
